quran[64]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Asizange yini sikunwebele (sikuvulele) isifuba sakho na
  94,2,Futhi sawususa kuwena umthwalo wakho
  94,3,Lowo owehlisela phansi umhlane wakho
  94,4,Futhi sakunyusela udumo lwakho
  94,5,"Manjalo, ngempela kanye nobunzima kunobulula"
  94,6,Futhi ngempela kanye nobunzima kunobulula
  94,7,Ngakho-ke uma usuqedile (umsebenzi wakho) sukuma (uphinde uthandaze)
  94,8,Futhi fisa eNkosini yakho
  95,1,Ngifunga ngekhiwane nangomhlwathi
  95,2,Futhi ngifunga ngentaba iSinayi
  95,3,Futhi ngifunga ngalelidolobha eliphephile (Makkah)
  95,4,Ngempela samdala umuntu ngokubunjwa (ngesimo) esihle kakhulu
  95,5,(Emva kwalokho) sabe sesimehlisela kokuphansi kakhulu
  95,6,"Ngaphandle kwalabo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo, manjalo okwabo ngumvuzo ongapheliyo"
  95,7,Ngokho-ke yini lena ekwenza uphike usuku lokwahlulela
  95,8,Akusiyena yini uMvelinqangi umehluleli wabehluleli na
  96,1,Funda ngegama leNkosi yakho eyadala
  96,2,Eyadala umuntu ngehlule
  96,3,"Funda, futhi iNkosi yakho inobubele kakhulu"
  96,4,Okuyiyona eyafundisa ngepeni lokubhala
  96,5,Yafundisa umuntu lokho angakwazi
  96,6,"Lutho!\tNgempela\tumuntu\twephula\tumthetho (kaMvelinqangi)"
  96,7,Uma ezibona ukuthi akadingi lutho
  96,8,Ngempela kuseNkosini yakho ukuphindela
  96,9,Ngakube umbonile yini lowo (u-Abujali)ovimba
  96,10,Inceku (umphrofethi) uma ithandaza
  96,11,Ngakube ubonile yini uma esekuholweni
  96,12,Noma ayale ngokulunga
  96,13,Ngakube ubonile yini uma ephika futhi efulathela (iqiniso)
  96,14,Akazi yini ukuthi uMvelinqangi uyabona
  96,15,"Lutho! Uma engaphezi, ngempela siyomdonsa ngesihlonti"
  96,16,Isiphongo esiqamba amanga esiyisoni
  96,17,Ngakho-ke akabize iqembu lakhe
  96,18,Siyobiza abaqaphi besihogo
  96,19,Lutho! Ungamhloniphi kodwa guqa phansi futhi usondele (kuMvelinqangi)
  97,1,"Ngempela\tsayethumela\tphansi\t(iQur’an)\tngobusuku obunqunyiwe"
  97,2,Futhi yini ekwenza wazi ukuthi yini ubusuku obunqunyiwe
  97,3,"Ubusuku\tobunamandla\tbungcono\tkunezinyanga eziyinkulungwane"
  97,4,Izingelosi kanye nomoya (uGabriyeli) zehlika ngabo (ubusuku obunamandla) ngemvume yeNKosi yazo nalolonke udaba
  97,5,Ukuthula yikona! Kuze kube ukuphakama kokusa
  98,1,Labo abangazange bakholwe abaphuma phakathi kwabantu bencwadi kanye nabakhonza izithombe abazange bayeke (ukukhonza izithombe) kwaze kwaba yilapho befikelwa ubufakazi obucacile
  98,2,Isithunywa esivela kuMvelinqangi sifunda imibhalo emsulwa
  98,3,Phakathi kunemibhalo eyiqiniso
  98,4,Futhi abazange baqembukelane labo ababenikezwe incwadi kwaze kwaba yingemumva kokuthi sekufike kubona ubufakazi obucacile
  98,5,"Futhi abazange baphoqwe ngaphandle kokuthi bakhonze uMvelinqangi babeqotho kuyena ngenkolo, babeneqiniso futhi benze umthandazo futhi banikele ngezakaah (ingxenye yengcebo ekhokhwa kwabampofu) futhi leyo yinkolo yeqiniso"
  98,6,"Ngempela labo abangazange bakholwe abaphuma phakathi kwabantu bencwadi nabakhonza izithixo bayokuba semlilweni wesihogo bayohlala phakathi kuwona ingunaphakade, labo- ke bona bayizidalwa ezimbi"
  98,7,Ngempela labo abakholwayo futhi abenza izenzo ezilungileyo labo-ke bona bayizidalwa ezinhle
  98,8,"Umvuzo wabo useNkosini yabo kuyoba yizivande zangunaphakade okugeleza ngaphansi kwazo imifula, bayohlala lapho phakathi ingunaphakade uMvelinqangi uyothokoza ngabo futhi bayothokoza ngaye, lokho okwanoma ngabe ngubani owesaba iNKosi yakhe"
  99,1,"Khumbula\tngenkathi\tuma\tumhlaba\tuyozama-zama ngokunyakaza kwawo"
  99,2,Futhi khumbula ngenkathi umhlaba ukhipha imithwalo yawo
  99,3,"Futhi khumbula umuntu uyothi, “kwenzekani ngawo”"
  99,4,Ngalolosuku uyokhuluma izindaba zawo
  99,5,Ngokuthi iNkosi yakho iyowushisekelisa
  99,6,"Ngalolosuku\tabantu\tbayoza\tbengamaqembu\tukuze bakhonjiswe izenzo zabo"
  99,7,Ngakho-ke noma ngabe ngubani owenza okungangesisindo esincane sokuhle uyokubona
  99,8,Futhi noma ngabe ngubani owenza okungangesisindo esincane sokubi uyokubona
  100,1,Ngifunga ngalokho okugijimayo (amahashi) okukhefuzelayo
  100,2,Okukhipha umlilo
  100,3,Amahashi ahlasela ekuseni
  100,4,Futhi ngifunga ngamahashi avusa uthuli
  100,5,Kanye nokufika lapho maphakathi beyisixuku
  100,6,Ngempela umuntu eNkosini yakhe akabongi
  100,7,Futhi ngempela yena kulokho ungufakazi
  100,8,Futhi ngempela yena usothandweni kakhulu lengcebo